text:
Hi guys, I"m trying to add a form to a banner/header in a module (generated by HubSpot, I"ve only added the class "form"), but somehow it only shows me the form_id and in-line message (see image). Below is the htmlHubL I'm using. How can I get a regular form visible here?
```{% if module.banner_title or module.banner_video %}
&lt;div class="banner" &gt;
  &lt;div class="banner_container" &gt;
    &lt;video src="{{ module.banner_video }}" playsinline autoplay loop muted&gt;&lt;/video&gt;
    &lt;div class="page-center"&gt;
      &lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{ module.banner_title }}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
      &lt;div class="form"&gt;
        {{ module.form_field }} &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;button class="scroll button-scroll"&gt;
        &lt;span&gt;{{ module.arrow_title }}&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="icon"&gt;
          &lt;span class="icon-bg"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class="arrows"&gt;
            &lt;svg xmlns="<http://www.w3.org/2000/svg>" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 20 20" class=""&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
{% endif %}  ```
